<COREF ID="33" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">The new president 's</COREF> inaugural ceremony</COREF> began at 9:00 am on 20 May at <COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">the Presidential Palace</COREF> .
