On the evening of <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">inauguration day</COREF> , <COREF ID="20" TYPE="IDENT">Chen Shui - bian</COREF> carried out two functions at <COREF ID="28" TYPE="IDENT">the Grand Hotel</COREF> .
